result.name: McDonald's

reviews.text: This place is so big that some ppl actually sleep in here. A place for homeless if u are not afraid of cold.
Nice place, the cheapest MC I ever saw and special offers and more varieties that I would like to have in Europe too.

As I started to enjoy my meal this afternoon in this McDonald, I realized there's some repair work going on. The repairman opened the ceiling panels one after the other and the nearest panel was just above my right shoulder. My tray of food was sprinkled with whatever that came off the ceiling. 
One McDonald's staff was standing next to the repairman and he completely agnore my complaint of inhygiene in the vicinity  and the repairman reacted with back talking.
I had to asked for the manager to explain the situation. Regrettably the female manager didn't seem to be bothered with the inhygiene problem and asked me to move to a table further away. 
Other foreign customers nearby gave me a couple of thumbs up while the situation developed... obviously they were bothered by these repair work while they were having their meals. Although I was given a new tray of clean food (hopefully ),  I don't think this McDonald's lives up to its reputation !
I love the breakfast at My Cafe.
Hot spot at Admiralty😊

result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 地點方便，能用最便宜的費用坐下，吃一杯軟雪糕，實在很抵食呀！👍👍
食品套餐比起駿發花園麥當勞貴些，例如開心樂園餐要22.50元，駿發麥當勞只需要20.50元！
買個早晨全餐啫，居然全部一早煮定，入口有種凍嘅感覺，超不爽！
呢間歷史悠久嘅分店以前係喺地庫，近幾年先至搬上地面。依家呢度嘅裝修比以前較有現代感同悠閒，冇以前喺地庫嗰陣咁迫同立立亂，加上有 McCafe，令食物嘅選擇多咗同質素有所提高。呢度雖位處彌敦道，但清早嘅人流唔多，係返工 / 放假時嘆早餐嘅好去處。

鳳梨的漢堡很好吃
凍檸茶很茶包味，不道地
